Lesson 1: Keep speccing in Mind for the next few levels.<P>Why?<BR>The Mind line is simply too good to put it aside: massive const/str debuff plus AE-mezz. Moreover it guarantees that you can go on charming mobs your level.<P>--------------------<P>Cay - Slave Driver on Gawaine
