<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Lesson 3: Check your pet's level<BR>Yellow mob does not equal yellow mob. Some of them are your level some are below. After successfully charming a mob check its/her/his level. You can see what level your pet is when you look at the 'pet-box'. To the right of the pet's name is its level in square brackets. So if you are level 10 and your pet is level [9] get rid of it and find another one. One level DOES make a huge difference.<P>--------------------<P>Cay - Slave Driver on Gawaine
</FONT>
