<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Lesson 4: Be evil treat your pet evilly.<BR>Your pet is your slave, if it HAD the chance it would wack you to kingdom come and back ... NEVER forget that. So if you make a bad pull and 3 instead of one mob comes your way: send your pet after one, mezz the others then IMMEDIATELY send your pet on each of the other mobs ... and as soon as your pet has aggro from all of them remezz ... NEVER take aggro yourself, somebody has to do the dirty job, make sure that somebody is never you   <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> <P>Oh, and step back ... IF your pet dies you can get another, if you die your will have to get another pet PLUS you lose exp and have to do a gravestone-run and pay for the const you lost (oh, remember lesson 2? group with a friar, they can rezz  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0">)<P>--------------------<P>Cay - Slave Driver on Gawaine
