Lesson 6: Chain 'nuke' at the right moment<BR>If you successfully pulled a single start chain nuking (if you specced in mind life-tab) the moment you can be sure the mob is VERY angry at your pet. Why? For one the mob will not aggro on you, moreover regenerating power takes way less than time than it takes your pet to get its hitpoints back, plus: the more damage you do the smaller is the chance your pet leeches experience.<P>--------------------<P>Cay - Slave Driver on Gawaine
