Lesson 8: Always remember Sorcerers are not the easiest class to play<P>Never forget you picked a class that takes a bit of brain to play well and that even getting a decent pet can be a demanding task at times. Sorcerer's are not thanes for instance (I play one [he is level 29] and I don't even get excited about killing two or even three yellows in one go anymore) -- they cannot tank, they die quickly, most groups don't understand their value (most groups have no brain /evil grin), they have to be wide awake at all times and most of all: playing a sorcerer is a challenge.<P>--------------------<P>Cay - Slave Driver on Gawaine
