Last i checked, shift-i showed both the mind blasts and life drains to have 2 second casting times.<P>Some people have claimed that life drain casts faster, but I have done a few tests by chain casting the same DD on a mob at maximum range until it gets to me.  With both the life drain and mind blast I have been able to get the same number of hits in.  And yes, I used the same mob type to make sure run speed did not affect it.<P>-Zanthis
